googlemaps-incompatible-browser: Ba meng akit ing mapang ibili king lugal a ini, kailangan me ing browser a makayagpang o maliari (compatible).
googlemaps-incompatible-browser-link: I-click me ini ba kang manakit tala/listaan da reng browsser a maliari/makayagpang (compatible).
googlemaps-no-editor: pagkalungkutan ming e la maliari king kekang browser deng kasangkapan a pangawang mapang interactive (interactive map-making features). Subukan me ing pekabayung bersion ning Internet Explorer (Windows) o Firefox (Windows, Mac, ampong Linux).
